:0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:02:20.000Z","msg":"廁田"},{"pid":"6bf91bcf5640e720f9ec0e9ccbd283b1691bd00e","tid":491683,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:02:37.000Z","msg":"珅哥"},{"pid":"27638bf941eb0c8b5939fff3fb74cc32c40c3410","tid":491683,"uid":134964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gem?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唱功係勁，初出道風格都正，但自從北上之後就得一種腔&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"761bbcba340986e1b5dfc4efde088c98aba5458c","tid":491683,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廁田</blockquote><br />\n的確"},{"pid":"ef2d519e54f707c7307bcbec2bc2b84bd676f6be","tid":491683,"uid":38369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:09:25.000Z","msg":"小肥？"},{"pid":"260f09419f0eb0c4c85329f219a753daf7d7de5d","tid":491683,"uid":134964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:09:50.000Z","msg":"新嗰批無人拍得住張敬軒，對上已經要數到鄭秀文林憶蓮張學友張國榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab77f9b7ea9e0fea6420eddb034d21d35c37649","tid":491683,"uid":80194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:13:38.000Z","msg":"佢首騷靈情歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0827c50d5efba01ab63c94953bebb98fd83d348","tid":491683,"uid":11320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:19:33.000Z","msg":"真正用技術，品行 服眾"},{"pid":"2bc71fce7b67c1b9f99dee520439056a6f0e6c07","tid":491683,"uid":136519,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:20:57.000Z","msg":"林子祥<br />\n李克勤<br />\n葉蒨文<br />\n張學友<br />\n林憶蓮<br />\n佢地嘅唱功其實都唔差，軒仔未贏得曬住。<br />\n林伯天生把聲真心正，高音渾厚，低音唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；其他個啲好似憶蓮、學友咁，本身把聲都J死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以加上後天練嘅技巧，佢地唱功係勁過軒仔。<br />\n克勤就技巧型，單論唱功例如控制、運氣方面，軒仔都仲需要學。但先此聲明，克勤係唱功整體好軒仔啲。但如果你計感情/鋪排/爆發，軒仔贏好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宋禮成首歌都可以係同一個tone，只不過高音令佢有少少起伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而整體黎計嘅話，我覺得軒仔都可以同林伯、學友憶蓮佢地比嘅。因為軒仔對於表達、舖排會比較着重，成首歌用嘅技巧感情都幾多樣化，所以佢會成日有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申1：非專業<br />\n利申2：上面個個都中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申3：張敬軒係我嘅bb豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585e0990fda733b1a67016b3e95c0f5b3452ce6b","tid":491683,"uid":31459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"鄭中基"},{"pid":"7e023f65bfd96b2fde03830862abf568dafdee50","tid":491683,"uid":103741,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"拍乳bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fd99c8b918de9552430ce4c5590d5656249414","tid":491683,"uid":65656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T22:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍乳bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地合唱果首騷靈情歌 <br />\n拍乳同hins簡直兩個level"},{"pid":"304b1b8992b0a72fdf5695266c50a872a10cfd34","tid":491683,"uid":149655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T22:42:59.000Z","msg":"次次聽張敬軒啲歌都聽到扯扯地"},{"pid":"ea285e9f05be57cb4fa241626baacd14f354cf7c","tid":491683,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"林俊傑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca575804c230b85b1fe3cb4e10c63901df46ba6","tid":49168